Description:
VENDOR WILL MEET THE MARKET.
Modern and exciting two bedroom residence, featuring caesar stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances, floating floors, heating & cooling, outstanding fittings and fixtures, plus single remote controlled garage. Step out into the great outdoors with pebble paving, well fenced low maintenance yard and a tranquil place to drink your morning coffee. Located in the Mornington Peninsula's booming and yet still tranquil Crib Point. Within walking distance to shops, St Joseph's Catholic Primary School and Crib Point Train Station. Only a 2 minute drive to HMAS Cerberus Naval Base and Stony Point ferry. Surrounded by some of the best beaches and wineries that the Mornington Peninsula has to offer such as Balnarring, Somers and Shoreham. Vacant Possession. Contact Agent Ken Brown on 0402 868 368 for further details.

Description:
EXQUISITE LIVING ON 1/4 ACRE
Beautifully presented four bedroom home offers the right mix for a modern lifestyle in a leafy 1/4 acre setting. Offering more than just the basics, this home has plenty of room to move and zones to grow. The design features what every family really needs, with four well placed bedrooms, separate rumpus room or kids retreat as well as an additional lounge area.
The main bedroom is tucked away with an ensuite that has handy access to a deck area looking out to the very private large backyard. A/C units are cleverly placed throughout the home and your eyes will immediately be drawn to the streamlined kitchen with wooden bench tops, large island bench and ample overhead cupboards; plus brand new S/S dishwasher, gas H/P, range hood and bench oven. Outside boasts double carport, workshop with ample shelving and storage, at the rear of the workshop is a very handy refurbished bungalow that is fully lined, new flooring and has a small separate sitting area which makes it ideal for a studio/study or teenager retreat. Access to the rear allowing for boat or caravan storage and landscape gardens enhance a very street appealing home. Still under Builders Warranty! A Certain Pleaser!

STAR QUALITY!
